@startuml users-schema
!theme plain
title Figure 3.3. Users Collection – Schema Detail

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
hide circle

skinparam class {
  BackgroundColor #E3F2FD
  BorderColor #1565C0
  HeaderBackgroundColor #1565C0
  HeaderFontColor white
}

class "users" <<MongoDB Collection>> {
  .. Primary Key ..
  **_id** : ObjectId <<auto-generated>>
  .. Required Fields ..
  **name** : String [required, maxlength: 100]
  **email** : String [required, unique, lowercase]
  **passwordHash** : String [required, minlength: 6, select: false]
  .. Role ..
  role : String [enum: "Admin" | "Manager" | "Teacher" | "Student", default: "Student"]
  .. Optional Fields ..
  avatar : String [default: ""]
  .. Status ..
  isActive : Boolean [default: true]
  .. Timestamps ..
  createdAt : Date [auto]
  updatedAt : Date [auto]
}

note right of "users"
  **Indexes:**
  - email: unique index
  - role: regular index

  **Password:**
  - Stored as bcrypt hash (salt rounds: 10)
  - Field hidden from queries (select: false)
  - Compared using comparePassword() method

  **Instance Methods:**
  - comparePassword(candidatePassword): boolean
  - toJSON(): Object (removes passwordHash)

  **Registration default:**
  - role = "Student"
  - isActive = true
end note

@enduml
